# Camagru Project Information
# Quick reference for development

## Project: Camagru - Social Media Photo Sharing
## Version: 1.0.0
## Date: December 2025
## School: 42

## Tech Stack
- PHP 8.1
- MySQL 8.0
- Docker & Docker Compose
- Vanilla JavaScript
- HTML5 Canvas

## Key Features
- Live camera capture
- 28+ interactive stickers (resize, rotate)
- 10+ emojis
- 7 Instagram-style filters
- Friend system
- 24-hour stories
- Direct messaging
- Email OTP verification

## Quick Commands
make help       # Show all commands
make build      # Build containers
make up         # Start services
make logs       # View logs
make status     # Check status

## URLs
http://localhost:8080  # Main application
http://localhost:8081  # PHPMyAdmin

